        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Redis — Cache & SignalR Backplane\nBacks the 60-second landlord-dashboard cache and the SignalR pub/sub backplane (real-time notifications). **Look here when:** dashboards feel slow, or real-time payment/invite notifications stop reaching browsers. Common red flags: `OOM`, `MISCONF`, persistence/`BGSAVE` failures, connection resets. Plain-text logs — panels use text matching."
      }
    },
